    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is an absolute gem and is in truly pristine condition\u2014it's been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a total dream and has been kept spotless inside and out. If you've been looking for a flawless vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 44500.0,
