    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E92 M3, powered by the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features a lightning-quick 8,400 RPM redline, managed by individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The longitudinal six-speed manual transmission delivers tactile engagement, while the M-Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal torque distribution. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing and throttle actuator service, the chassis exhibits zero structural fatigue. The factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system and subframe bushings are in peak operational condition, offering a visceral yet refined driving dynamic. A pristine example for the discerning enthusiast seeking mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
