    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and subjected to a rigorous professional detailing regimen, including a multi-stage paint correction and ceramic coating. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark in sight. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear, and that distinct new-car scent still lingers. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all fluids recently flushed and a fresh set of high-performance tires. We have all original documentation, including the window sticker and both factory keys. This is quite simply the finest example currently on the market, perfect for the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
